com.ibm.team.process.common.advice
Interface IItemsResponse

public interface IItemsResponse

Operation response which carries a collection of persisted items (IItem).

This response object should not be used for non-persisted, modeled objects (DTOs).

IObjectsResponse should be used to transmit non-persisted objects (DTOs).

Since:
0.5
